                    <i class="house"></i>冯家峪镇
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="208690916">
            这个小山包就是独秀峰。<br />
<br />
计划中，先看上峪古堡和千年古槐树，可到这里也没看到上峪的指示牌，莫非走错了？我们又前行了一段路，大概是何家店村。看到一辆警车从村里驶出，我就向警察打听上峪古城怎么走，是否有古槐树。<br />
警察同志回答挺干脆，说你走过了，离这里有3.4公里，并说跟我走吧，说完开车就走。<br />
我不敢怠慢，赶紧跟上，好家伙，这条路经过村庄限速40公里，可警车开的速度很快，我开快了怕违章，开慢了怕掉队，进退两难。<br />
好在只有3公里多，警车先停在叉路口，看我车过来，用手一指道路然后开走了，这里再次感谢公安干警同志。
        </p>
            <div data-seq="208805463" data-index="1" class="article_title _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem">
                <h2 class="t6"><span class="_j_anchor">上峪古堡</span></h2>
            </div>
            <div id="_j_photo_208697761" data-seq="208697767" data-pid="208697761" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="18771367">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_6992372/208697761.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:510px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://c2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/3B/50/wKgBZ1kUX1OAFNeOABbpzZQ_tzU49.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90" data-rt-src="https://c2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/3B/50/wKgBZ1kUX1OAFNeOABbpzZQ_tzU49.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90" data-pid="208697761" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a style="cursor:default" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="18771367" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="house"></i>上峪古堡
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="208698469">
            上峪村位于<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/13571.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="密云" target="_blank">密云</a>冯家峪镇西约2公里，<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/13571.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="密云" target="_blank">密云</a>上峪古堡据当地村民讲为当年秦始皇修边时所建，最初由秦始皇时期兵屯的一个马厩演变而来，后来在明万历年间做过修补。不过依古树和古堡的完整程度，它的历史并非那么久远。《<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/13571.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="密云" target="_blank">密云</a>县地名志》中对它的记录是“建于明朝永乐年间，补修于万历年间”，倒与“先有核槐后有城”的说法相印证。村口有古核桃树和古槐树各一株。当地传说先有核槐后有城。该城堡只有一个城门。城门洞上原有老爷庙一座，已毁。还有娘娘庙一座，据说供奉的是眼光娘娘，庙舍尚存。古堡城墙石条有些当年在修建半城子水库被拆走。现古堡遗迹已被保护，为<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/13571.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="密云" target="_blank">密云</a>县文物保护单位。&nbsp;站在上峪古堡跟前，远山上耸立的烽火台清晰可见。
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_208697762" data-seq="208697768" data-pid="208697762" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="18771367">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_6992372/208697762.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:510px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://c3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/3B/53/wKgBZ1kUX1qAMUTjABYfHRtX_Rs75.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90" data-rt-src="https://c3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/3B/53/wKgBZ1kUX1qAMUTjABYfHRtX_Rs75.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90" data-pid="208697762" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a style="cursor:default" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="18771367" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
