            <div id="_j_photo_208804795" data-seq="208804806" data-pid="208804795" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="6628694">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_6992372/208804795.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:510px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://a4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/76/05/wKgBZ1kVKLSAAgeQABCj1mRwGLI81.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90" data-rt-src="https://a4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/76/05/wKgBZ1kVKLSAAgeQABCj1mRwGLI81.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90" data-pid="208804795" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/poi/6628694.html" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="6628694" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="house"></i>密云番字牌石刻
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <div id="_j_photo_208804796" data-seq="208804807" data-pid="208804796" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="6628694">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_6992372/208804796.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:510px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://n2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/76/08/wKgBZ1kVKLmAG9MeAA6GXnFgjrU75.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90" data-rt-src="https://n2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/76/08/wKgBZ1kVKLmAG9MeAA6GXnFgjrU75.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90" data-pid="208804796" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/poi/6628694.html" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="6628694" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="house"></i>密云番字牌石刻
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <div id="_j_photo_208804797" data-seq="208804808" data-pid="208804797" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="6628694">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_6992372/208804797.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:510px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://n4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/76/0C/wKgBZ1kVKL2ATwzEAA2Evyca5FQ60.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90" data-rt-src="https://n4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/76/0C/wKgBZ1kVKL2ATwzEAA2Evyca5FQ60.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90" data-pid="208804797" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/poi/6628694.html" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="6628694" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="house"></i>密云番字牌石刻
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <div id="_j_photo_208804798" data-seq="208804809" data-pid="208804798" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="6628694">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_6992372/208804798.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:510px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://b3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/76/0F/wKgBZ1kVKMGAL0XmAAsG_P--GlU05.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90" data-rt-src="https://b3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/76/0F/wKgBZ1kVKMGAL0XmAAsG_P--GlU05.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90" data-pid="208804798" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/poi/6628694.html" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="6628694" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="house"></i>密云番字牌石刻
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="208832970">
            1987年经<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/21536.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="中国" target="_blank">中国</a>科学院民族研究所的专家们鉴定：&nbsp;石壁上的番字系北方少数民族的文字。其中，有梵文(古<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10069.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="尼泊尔" target="_blank">尼泊尔</a>文)、蒙文和藏文，文字的内容是佛教的“六字真言”。在东山坡上，有一块高2米多的立石，石的东面石壁上刻有一个大型番字，字高1米有余，宽约30厘米，为佛教的“十自在画”。刻字的时间为明清时代。为<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/13571.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="密云" target="_blank">密云</a>县重点保护文物。
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_208804799" data-seq="208804810" data-pid="208804799" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="6628694">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_6992372/208804799.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:510px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://p4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/76/12/wKgBZ1kVKMWAfEy1AAzh4RoXP-E38.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90" data-rt-src="https://p4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/76/12/wKgBZ1kVKMWAfEy1AAzh4RoXP-E38.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90" data-pid="208804799" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/poi/6628694.html" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="6628694" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="house"></i>密云番字牌石刻
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
    
</div>
